<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:Yossi_Vardi,_2005.jpg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"><img src="/skins-1.5/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
Yossi Vardi in 2005</div>
