<p><b>Joseph (Yossi) Vardi</b> (<a href="/wiki/Hebrew_language" title="Hebrew language">Hebrew</a>: <span lang="he" dir="rtl" xml:lang="he">יוסי ורדי</span>‎), born in 1942, is one of <a href="/wiki/Israel" title="Israel">Israel</a>'s early tech <a href="/wiki/Entrepreneur" title="Entrepreneur">entrepreneurs</a>. For 40 years he founded and helped build over 50 tech companies in diverse areas of software, energy, <a href="/wiki/Internet" title="Internet">Internet</a>, mobile, <a href="/wiki/Electro-optics" title="Electro-optics">electro-optics</a>, clean water and others.</p>
